data.title: Live Music by Scott, Rob, and Greg of The Clarks
data.meta_description:
Jam out Saturday night with live music by members Scott, Rob, and Greg of The Clarks - a Pittsburgh-native rock band!

We have complimentary wine tastings, and if wine isn't your thing, we carry local craft beer and local spirits for cocktails!

The Lunch Lady on Wheels and Armida's Cucina food trucks will be on site.

Please call (724)-446-5000 for reservations* or more information. Reservations are recommended for this event to secure a spot!

*Due to limited parking space, there is a $5 parking fee per car. We encourage carpooling!
